  "summary": "Mafia is a psychological game played in a group, similar to Werewolf or Assassin. It takes strategic role playing to a whole new level. With the Mafia App, it’s easy to learn how to play Mafia. Each person in your group is randomly — and secretly — assigned a role, such as Mafia, Police, Doctor, Spy, Prostitute, and more. The peaceful Citizens try to figure out who has the Mafia role and eliminate them. The Mafia tries to eliminate Citizens. With each turn, tensions rise. Everybody claims to not be Mafia. But some of you are lying…",
